            "tag": "Customer favourite",
            "heading": "Geranium & Ylang Ylang",
            "details": "Warm, woody ho wood complements herbaceous hints of geranium and rich tones of ylang ylang.",
            "expend-label": "blend details",
            "expendable-content": "<div>\n    <h4 class=\"font-lausanne\">Middle notes</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Ho Wood</span>\n            <br>\n          Sweet, fresh and woody\n        </li>\n<li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Geranium</span>\n            <br>\n          Rosy, floral and uplifting\n        </li>\n<li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Coriander seed</span>\n            <br>\n          Herbaceous and spicy\n        </li>\n<li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Clary Sage</span>\n            <br>\n          Distinctive and sweet\n        </li>\n<li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n            <span class=\"fw-400\">Ylang-Ylang</span>\n            <br>\n          Heady and rich\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n</div>"
          }
        },
